highlights.text: Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Chennai. Thenmozhi (From "Thiruchitrambalam") is the highest at #4.
Raja Raja Cholan - Rettai Vaal Kuruvi - Tamil by Roshan Sebastian and Robin Sebastian is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chennai, up 60 spots at #35.
Nee Paartha Vizhigal - The Touch of Love by Anirudh Ravichander, Vijay Yesudas, and Shweta Mohan has been on Top Songs Chennai the longest, at 52 weeks straight.
Yaarum illa (From "Naane Varuvean") by Anthony Daasan, Yuvan Shankar Raja, and Vivek is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chennai at #93.
